{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f7bf87935e","title":"农村小医院","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"07ca61680b","index":0,"year":1958,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"f7bf87935e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","name":"红旗一九五八年第八期","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"22f5edebb5","name":"中共应城县委会"}]},"publication_details":{"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"69b48bf1cf","type":"paragraph","text":"活动；烽火农业补这一面红族，推动了全省的科学研究工作。特别层通过整风运动学会了朵用大鸣、大放、大争、大异、大字报的方法，来进行政治教育和宜传鼓动工作，从根本f改变了那种照本宣科的注人式数学方法和单辅依施干部、群众听的宜传方法。这是宣传教育方法上的一大革命。","index":0,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"59405d3bf6","type":"paragraph","text":"飞年以来直传交教工作中还存在着一些缺点。比更要的是对教条主义、修正主义的批判还不够彻底。有些部周的工作于劲还不大，信心还不足，风格还不高，缺","index":1,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"3b508a0c98","type":"paragraph","text":"农村小医院","index":2,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"ad8ce258f8","type":"paragraph","text":"湖北省稀水县红建乡群英农业就，在今年七月下旬办起了一个小医院。当时，经有七十多天没下透雨了，眼看田里至部断了水，需要天力抗是。司是，正当这个紧急的时候，有三十多个就员中害、海让、伤风一个.个地病倒了。每个病人，需要-·个人来清医年，买药和额，全贰一一百九-1个劳动力，下子就长了六十多个。这一夹可把社主任款坏广，少不得商乡党委求候。乡觉委除向各计抽入协助以外，还指示他们应当白已多想办法。耐主任被乡党泛力维游、力筝第一的思想。有些部门在工作中彻群众路不够，比校突出的表现是一些交艺团体没有大胞地向工农开门。另外，还有多新的周题尚末得到很好的解决，例如，生产大跃进以来，学校","index":3,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"93d9975ad4","type":"paragraph","text":"中的计多课程内容急需改革，有的甚至","index":4,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"5f6ea4a63b","type":"paragraph","text":"数不下去了（例如，有些农业课和文史），而我们的数学改革还没有迅速地赶上去，等等。这些缺点和间题都是需要进一步加以克服和解决的。","index":5,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"b3f95ec7f9","type":"paragraph","text":"（幅老本交作者是中共陕西省委会补害配）","index":6,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"a9454eea73","type":"paragraph","text":"过县委的领导，很快地在全区推广，不到牛个月，全区一百→十个合作就大体上都办想水了。医务人具和社量们，办小医院","index":7,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"c503561c00","type":"paragraph","text":"有几大好处：赵振恒","index":8,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"893999bc9e","type":"paragraph","text":"第一，节省大批劳动力，提高了代勤率。有了小医院，不但","index":9,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"bce08ca1b7","type":"paragraph","text":"大大节省了照病人的人力，而委一付酷提硬了，他想：“赶里","index":10,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"610ee623a8","type":"paragraph","text":"且航短了治疗时间。过去在家能办集体食堂，为什么不能办个","index":11,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"f13aea3ad6","type":"paragraph","text":"里病，医疗不及时，生活照小医院呢？于是在乡卫生院的","index":12,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"c4e6873aa3","type":"paragraph","text":"不周到，病人汉往往欲食不当，协助下，腾出两间房子，用石灰","index":13,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"e635d29152","type":"paragraph","text":"因此，就拖长了治疗时间。群笑刷一下，打了滑毒水。除保健晶","index":14,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"51b80096b3","type":"paragraph","text":"农业耐在散院前，在家轮病时，外，又增加一个护理。又买了","index":15,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"be9c4fd6b5","type":"paragraph","text":"平均每个病人，七火才能治儿元路的黏品，专门准备了些细","index":16,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"ced89aa12f","type":"paragraph","text":"好，在小医院病以后，不均每粮和蛋、白椅。于是把病人都","index":17,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"2bc5eb296f","type":"paragraph","text":"人只一天就好了。主乡根据动量到小医院来什下。乡医院分","index":18,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"399df5049d","type":"paragraph","text":"第-疗程治愈的百五+个工到这个叶治病的医生，大来","index":19,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"1cd9d0566c","type":"paragraph","text":"病人舒算，就节省了二平九百九看几次。这样，病人得到了舒适","index":20,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"8fdb5e5329","type":"paragraph","text":"十多个工，出勤率提高百分之十的护理，护理的人从三于多个减","index":21,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"cebacaf2d0","type":"paragraph","text":"五以上。往年年秘结算时，一找为两个，大批劳动力又量新投","index":22,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"4dab795c37","type":"paragraph","text":"超支片超支的原因，一牛无右是人了抗量斗等。","index":23,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"bea9c658b3","type":"paragraph","text":"害病澳工造成的，“小医院*戴把群英耐办小医院的辐，","index":24,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"9c0184a90b","type":"paragraph","text":"这个周题解决了。","index":25,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"8287ea7120","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，便利群众，提商了生产积极性。过去群众流传一句农蒂：“一人害病，至家不安。北永乡三泉二科县李天然是个单身汉，他的父亲已经六十多岁。前些时候李天然病了，他父亲到十果路外的多医院请医生，一跟-拐跑了一天，病人无人料理，差一点把老头也累倒.后来，耐里办起小医院，李天然进院了，这老头高兴得速叫毛主席万岁。天然乡兴除就贰量李光发病了，送到小医院后，他一进医院很惊奇地：“这里又清洁，又没有孩子肺，比家里好多了。我走到这里，病就好了三分。”最近，中普漏流传着“小病不休息，中病不出就，大病不出乡，今后再不怕有病了。”总之，有了小医院，病人照额好了，家也能安心生产了。.第兰，节约了用费，减少了开支。赶乡群众社在没有小医院时，每个病人不均用钱一元五角二，有了小医院，每人不均只用三角疑。天然乡河，往日一个月病人开支要三百元，有了小医院一个月平均只用二十多元就够了。","index":26,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"47e6f525df","type":"paragraph","text":"第四，治疗及时，提高了治疗效果，多医院的医生过去也分片包于，一个医生一般鱼相三至四个社，每天要跑一通，这三、四个社总是几十个病人，往往跑不过来，医生整天跑路，东额不了西，医疗工作也就难免粗一些。果轻病变成重病，引超了群众理。“小医院”成立以","index":27,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"d7d61719e5","type":"paragraph","text":"染病，往往是全家，全村传染。后，医生一天只跑三、四个地方，","index":28,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"d57aecb648","type":"paragraph","text":"病人住到小医院以后，对制止疾不值治疗及时，而且可以平心静","index":29,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"7709577ad3","type":"paragraph","text":"病蔓延和传染病流行，起了极大气地坐下来，细致地观察掌提病","index":30,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"f1986f07ad","type":"paragraph","text":"的作用。情，治疗效果也就自然提商了。","index":31,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"0528479aed","type":"paragraph","text":"第七，医务人量有了充分的第五，培养了农村中的卫生","index":32,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"fff2c68990","type":"paragraph","text":"学习和研究时间。过去，虽然乡事业人材。过去每个社虽然股","index":33,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"6ebf6d7e7a","type":"paragraph","text":"里成立了乡医院，但医生整天化了保健量，但由于分散治疗，医","index":34,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"dd66b0c481","type":"paragraph","text":"子到各耐各家“出差”，对乡医院生和保健往往脱节，保健员很","index":35,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"6e8d412260","type":"paragraph","text":"照不过来。现在不但可以对难在业务提高。所以群众叫","index":36,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"fb2140c6cd","type":"paragraph","text":"多医院多照些，而且有时间学保健哥是“红黄弹酒，扶了就","index":37,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"f4d7d464f6","type":"paragraph","text":"习政治和业务了，这当然使他走”。小医院成立以后，保健","index":38,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"1fcffaeb2a","type":"paragraph","text":"提高的也快了。许多医生反映常常和医生在一起工作，可以边","index":39,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"ac9f33036d","type":"paragraph","text":"：“红专开题，现在才找到了做边学。通过实践，业务技术很","index":40,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"288144ac31","type":"paragraph","text":"解决的机会。快提高了。如北永乡的小医院","index":41,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"55859195f3","type":"paragraph","text":"最后，有效地制止了一小部成立不到牛个月，全乡十一个保","index":42,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"1bfb9d7dd0","type":"paragraph","text":"分社量的做价装病行为。红建乡健有十一个学会注射，般都","index":43,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"8b5d1ec9aa","type":"paragraph","text":"群勇社有个富裕中农朱又林，生学会影渐八、九种病，学会用二","index":44,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"fafbf616dd","type":"paragraph","text":"产一微消极。他有点螺微的置十多种药。不少病，保健最就可","index":45,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"01b4cbf17e","type":"paragraph","text":"病，叫医生开了个方子，带在身以动手治疗了。天然乡红星社上整天不出工。别人要间他，他保健量孟群民，在医院成立的五","index":46,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"68dbcf40ce","type":"paragraph","text":"把莉方拿到别人脸上一见：天内，就治好八十七个病人。","index":47,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"2395dcea1b","type":"paragraph","text":"“看！这不是医生开的病方，我难红建乡群安能保健员包子安，可","index":48,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"2f3c6d781e","type":"paragraph","text":"道会装病不成？”这次小医院成以款到十多种病，并且把病人的","index":49,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"ec1834746d","type":"paragraph","text":"立以后，他这个计”一下予伙食办得很好。社昌称赞他“","index":50,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"4f8e441997","type":"paragraph","text":"失效了。有一些装的人，货郎卖花，百事有”。有很多社除","index":51,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"5d31425940","type":"paragraph","text":"送到医院被检查出来以后，经过了保链复，还我一个护理量，现","index":52,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"b3986fd9f1","type":"paragraph","text":"耐干部的教育又参加了生产。在一般护理的水平，可以抵上","index":53,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"5a60c8fd21","type":"paragraph","text":"现在“小医院”在群众中的过去的一个保健员。这就翰农","index":54,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"5bced2425f","type":"paragraph","text":"威信-天比一天高，有还准村卫生事业大发腰，培养与准备","index":55,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"8a76d8c702","type":"paragraph","text":"备办常年小医隆，看来这好象是","index":56,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"0c95b24a07","type":"paragraph","text":"一件小事，但实际是群众生活中了大批的人材。","index":57,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"b4955506fe","type":"paragraph","text":"第六，病人得到了隔离，防","index":58,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"f4e6f8cb15","type":"paragraph","text":"的一件大事。可以，这也是共止了传染。过去农民家中有了","index":59,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"6a5871d987","type":"paragraph","text":"产主义幸福生活的萌之一病人，在料理病人时，经常接近","index":60,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"c3e69acbcc","type":"paragraph","text":"也阻挡不了它变成大树，开花精病人，病人吃剩的东西，也往往果，兴旺起来。叫别人吃掉，病人用过的东两不","index":61,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"9730158f3f","type":"paragraph","text":"（老按：本文作春是中共知精毒。因而一遇到流行性传","index":62,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"},{"id":"348bd13ec6","type":"paragraph","text":"潘水县委会香纪处害起）","index":63,"publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e"}],"page":{"id":"900dda394b","publicationId":"ec8fd1ff-a1c1-4a67-8c30-d40e168f0fe4","articleId":"f7bf87935e","start":39,"end":40}}}},"__N_SSG":true}